title: Ebro In The Morning - Happy (Late) Birthday Rosenberg + Rolling Loud Drama

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/25/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Keke Palmer-Zendaya drama, Rosenberg's Birthday, Rolling Loud, and much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
